  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the grill to medium-high heat.",
    "Thread the spring onions onto skewers.",
    "In a bowl, mix together olive oil, garlic powder, paprika, salt, and black pepper.",
    "Brush the mixture onto the spring onions.",
    "Grill the skewers for 5 minutes per side.",
    "Meanwhile, mix together parsley, lemon juice, and water in a bowl.",
    "Once the skewers are done, brush them with the parsley mixture.",
    "Serve the skewers warm."
